            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-479] QuorumHierarchical does not count groups correctly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-479</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;QuorumHierarchical::containsQuorum should not verify if all groups represented in the input set have more than half of the total weight. Instead, it should check only for an overall majority of groups. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
